&lt;p style=&quot;color: rgb(33, 37, 41);&quot;&gt;Given:&amp;nbsp;&lt;strong&gt;15 August 2006&lt;/strong&gt;&lt;span style=&quot;font-weight: bolder;&quot;&gt;&amp;nbsp;was Tuesday&lt;/span&gt;.&lt;/p&gt;

&lt;p style=&quot;color: rgb(33, 37, 41);&quot;&gt;Now,&lt;/p&gt;

&lt;p style=&quot;color: rgb(33, 37, 41);&quot;&gt;2006&amp;nbsp;to 2011&amp;nbsp;= 5&amp;nbsp;Years (4 Ordinary Years and 1 Leap Year).&lt;/p&gt;

&lt;p style=&quot;color: rgb(33, 37, 41);&quot;&gt;And, In 5&amp;nbsp;Years = 1&amp;nbsp;Leap year and 4&amp;nbsp;Ordinary Years.&lt;/p&gt;

&lt;p style=&quot;color: rgb(33, 37, 41);&quot;&gt;So, 1 Leap Year has 2 odd days,&lt;/p&gt;

&lt;p style=&quot;color: rgb(33, 37, 41);&quot;&gt;And, 4&amp;nbsp;Ordinary Years&amp;nbsp;have 4&amp;nbsp;odd days.&lt;/p&gt;

&lt;p style=&quot;color: rgb(33, 37, 41);&quot;&gt;Total odd days = 2 + 4&amp;nbsp;= 6.&lt;/p&gt;

&lt;p style=&quot;color: rgb(33, 37, 41);&quot;&gt;6&amp;nbsp;odd days &amp;rarr; 6/7 = 0 weeks and 6&amp;nbsp;odd days.&lt;/p&gt;

&lt;p style=&quot;color: rgb(33, 37, 41);&quot;&gt;then,&amp;nbsp;&lt;span style=&quot;font-weight: bolder;&quot;&gt;15 August 2011&amp;nbsp;will be Tuesday + 6&amp;nbsp;= Monday&lt;/span&gt;.&lt;/p&gt;

&lt;p style=&quot;color: rgb(33, 37, 41);&quot;&gt;Now, the number of days between&amp;nbsp;&lt;span style=&quot;&quot;&gt;15 August 2011&lt;/span&gt;&amp;nbsp;to&amp;nbsp;19 February 2012&lt;/p&gt;

&lt;p style=&quot;color: rgb(33, 37, 41);&quot;&gt;= 16(August) + 30(September) + 31(October) + 30(November) + 31(December) + 31(January) + 19(February) = 188 days.&lt;/p&gt;

&lt;p style=&quot;color: rgb(33, 37, 41);&quot;&gt;= 188&amp;nbsp;days&amp;nbsp;&amp;rarr; 188/7 = 26&amp;nbsp;weeks and 6&amp;nbsp;odd days.&lt;/p&gt;

&lt;p style=&quot;color: rgb(33, 37, 41);&quot;&gt;So,&amp;nbsp;&lt;strong&gt;&lt;span style=&quot;color: rgb(33, 37, 41);&quot;&gt;19 February 2012&lt;/span&gt;&lt;/strong&gt;&lt;span style=&quot;font-weight: bolder;&quot;&gt; will be&amp;nbsp;&lt;/span&gt;&lt;span style=&quot;color: rgb(33, 37, 41); font-weight: 700;&quot;&gt;Monday&amp;nbsp;&lt;/span&gt;&lt;span style=&quot;font-weight: bolder;&quot;&gt;+ 6&amp;nbsp;= Sunday.&lt;/span&gt;&lt;/p&gt;

&lt;p style=&quot;color: rgb(33, 37, 41);&quot;&gt;Hence, the correct answer is&amp;nbsp;&lt;span style=&quot;font-weight: bolder;&quot;&gt;&amp;quot;Option 3&amp;quot;&lt;/span&gt;.&lt;/p&gt;

