&lt;p style=&quot;color: rgb(33, 37, 41);&quot;&gt;&lt;strong&gt;Given:&lt;/strong&gt;&amp;nbsp;6 May 2005&lt;span style=&quot;font-weight: bolder;&quot;&gt;&amp;nbsp;was Friday&lt;/span&gt;.&lt;/p&gt;

&lt;p style=&quot;color: rgb(33, 37, 41);&quot;&gt;Now,&lt;/p&gt;

&lt;p style=&quot;color: rgb(33, 37, 41);&quot;&gt;2005&amp;nbsp;to 2018&amp;nbsp;= 13&amp;nbsp;Years (10 Ordinary Years and 3 Leap Years).&lt;/p&gt;

&lt;p style=&quot;color: rgb(33, 37, 41);&quot;&gt;And, In 13&amp;nbsp;Years = 3&amp;nbsp;Leap years and 10&amp;nbsp;Ordinary Years.&lt;/p&gt;

&lt;p style=&quot;color: rgb(33, 37, 41);&quot;&gt;So, 3 Leap Years have 6 odd days,&lt;/p&gt;

&lt;p style=&quot;color: rgb(33, 37, 41);&quot;&gt;And, 10&amp;nbsp;Ordinary Years&amp;nbsp;have 10&amp;nbsp;odd days.&lt;/p&gt;

&lt;p style=&quot;color: rgb(33, 37, 41);&quot;&gt;Total odd days = 6 + 10&amp;nbsp;= 16.&lt;/p&gt;

&lt;p style=&quot;color: rgb(33, 37, 41);&quot;&gt;16&amp;nbsp;odd days &amp;rarr; 16/7 = 2 weeks and 2&amp;nbsp;odd days.&lt;/p&gt;

&lt;p style=&quot;color: rgb(33, 37, 41);&quot;&gt;then,&amp;nbsp;&lt;span style=&quot;font-weight: bolder;&quot;&gt;6 May 2018&amp;nbsp;will be Friday + 2&amp;nbsp;= Sunday&lt;/span&gt;.&lt;/p&gt;

&lt;p style=&quot;color: rgb(33, 37, 41);&quot;&gt;Now, the number of days between&amp;nbsp;&lt;span style=&quot;&quot;&gt;6 May 2018&lt;/span&gt;&amp;nbsp;to&amp;nbsp;25 September 2018&lt;/p&gt;

&lt;p style=&quot;color: rgb(33, 37, 41);&quot;&gt;= 25(May)&amp;nbsp;+ 30(June) + 31(July) + 31(August) + 25(September) = 142 days.&lt;/p&gt;

&lt;p style=&quot;color: rgb(33, 37, 41);&quot;&gt;= 142 days&amp;nbsp;&amp;rarr; 142/7 = 20 weeks and 2&amp;nbsp;odd days.&lt;/p&gt;

&lt;p style=&quot;color: rgb(33, 37, 41);&quot;&gt;So,&amp;nbsp;&lt;strong&gt;&lt;span style=&quot;color: rgb(33, 37, 41);&quot;&gt;25 September 2018&lt;/span&gt;&lt;/strong&gt;&lt;span style=&quot;font-weight: bolder;&quot;&gt; will be&amp;nbsp;&lt;/span&gt;&lt;span style=&quot;color: rgb(33, 37, 41); font-weight: 700;&quot;&gt;Sunday&amp;nbsp;&lt;/span&gt;&lt;span style=&quot;font-weight: bolder;&quot;&gt;+ 2&amp;nbsp;= Tuesday.&lt;/span&gt;&lt;/p&gt;

&lt;p style=&quot;color: rgb(33, 37, 41);&quot;&gt;Hence, the correct answer is&amp;nbsp;&lt;span style=&quot;font-weight: bolder;&quot;&gt;&amp;quot;Option 3&amp;quot;&lt;/span&gt;.&lt;/p&gt;

