&lt;p&gt;Select the set in which the numbers are related in the same way as are the numbers of the following sets.&lt;/p&gt;

&lt;p&gt;(NOTE : Operations should be performed on the whole numbers, without breaking down the numbers into its constituent digits. E.g. 13 &amp;ndash; Operations on 13 such as adding /subtracting /multiplying etc. to 13 can be performed. Breaking down 13 into 1 and 3 and then performing mathematical operations on 1 and 3 is not allowed)&lt;/p&gt;

&lt;p&gt;(21, 34, 76)&lt;/p&gt;

&lt;p&gt;(39, 26, 104)&lt;/p&gt;

questions.explanation:
&lt;p style=&quot;color: rgb(33, 37, 41);&quot;&gt;&lt;strong&gt;The logic followed here is:&lt;/strong&gt;&lt;/p&gt;

&lt;p style=&quot;color: rgb(33, 37, 41);&quot;&gt;&lt;strong&gt;Logic:&amp;nbsp;&lt;/strong&gt;&lt;span style=&quot;font-weight: bolder;&quot;&gt;(1st number&amp;nbsp;&lt;/span&gt;&lt;span style=&quot;font-weight: bolder;&quot;&gt;&amp;times; 2) + second number&amp;nbsp;&lt;/span&gt;&lt;span style=&quot;font-weight: bolder;&quot;&gt;= 3rd number&lt;/span&gt;.&lt;/p&gt;

&lt;p style=&quot;color: rgb(33, 37, 41);&quot;&gt;Now,&lt;/p&gt;

&lt;p style=&quot;color: rgb(33, 37, 41);&quot;&gt;For,&amp;nbsp;(21, 34, 76)&lt;/p&gt;

&lt;p&gt;&amp;rArr; (21 &amp;times; 2) + 34&lt;/p&gt;

&lt;p&gt;&lt;span style=&quot;color: rgb(33, 37, 41);&quot;&gt;&amp;rArr;&lt;/span&gt;&amp;nbsp;42 + 34 = 76.&lt;/p&gt;

&lt;p&gt;For,&amp;nbsp;(39, 26, 104)&lt;/p&gt;

&lt;p style=&quot;color: rgb(33, 37, 41);&quot;&gt;&amp;rArr; (39&amp;nbsp;&amp;times; 2) + 26&lt;/p&gt;

&lt;p style=&quot;color: rgb(33, 37, 41);&quot;&gt;&amp;rArr; 78&amp;nbsp;+ 26&amp;nbsp;= 104.&lt;/p&gt;

&lt;p style=&quot;color: rgb(33, 37, 41);&quot;&gt;Similarly, for &lt;strong&gt;Option 2: (28, 23, 79)&lt;/strong&gt;&lt;/p&gt;

&lt;p&gt;&lt;strong&gt;&amp;rArr; (28 &amp;times; 2) + 23 &lt;/strong&gt;&lt;/p&gt;

&lt;p&gt;&lt;strong&gt;&lt;span style=&quot;color: rgb(33, 37, 41);&quot;&gt;&amp;rArr;&lt;/span&gt;&amp;nbsp;56 + 23 = 79&lt;/strong&gt;&lt;/p&gt;

&lt;p style=&quot;color: rgb(33, 37, 41);&quot;&gt;Hence, the correct answer is&amp;nbsp;&lt;span style=&quot;font-weight: bolder;&quot;&gt;&amp;quot;Option 2&amp;quot;&lt;/span&gt;.&lt;/p&gt;

&lt;p style=&quot;color: rgb(33, 37, 41);&quot;&gt;&lt;strong&gt;BODMAS Table:&amp;nbsp;&lt;/strong&gt;&lt;/p&gt;

&lt;p style=&quot;color: rgb(33, 37, 41);&quot;&gt;&lt;img alt=&quot;&quot; src=&quot;//cdn.testbook.com/images/production/quesImages/qImage14137.png&quot; /&gt;&lt;/p&gt;

&lt;p style=&quot;color: rgb(33, 37, 41);&quot;&gt;&lt;strong&gt;Given equation:&lt;/strong&gt;&amp;nbsp;14 + 6 &amp;times; 3 &amp;divide; 7 - 2 = ?&lt;/p&gt;

&lt;p style=&quot;color: rgb(33, 37, 41);&quot;&gt;Now,&amp;nbsp;if &amp;lsquo;+&amp;rsquo; and &amp;lsquo;-&amp;lsquo; interchanged and &amp;lsquo;&amp;times;&amp;#39; and &amp;#39;&amp;divide;&amp;rsquo; are interchanged, then:&lt;/p&gt;

&lt;p style=&quot;color: rgb(33, 37, 41);&quot;&gt;&amp;rArr;&amp;nbsp;14 -&amp;nbsp;&lt;u&gt;&lt;strong&gt;6 &amp;divide; 3&lt;/strong&gt;&lt;/u&gt; &amp;times; 7 +&amp;nbsp;2 = ?&lt;/p&gt;

&lt;p style=&quot;color: rgb(33, 37, 41);&quot;&gt;&amp;rArr; 14 - &lt;u&gt;&lt;strong&gt;2&amp;nbsp;&amp;times; 7&lt;/strong&gt;&lt;/u&gt; + 2 = ?&lt;/p&gt;

&lt;p style=&quot;color: rgb(33, 37, 41);&quot;&gt;&amp;rArr; &lt;u&gt;&lt;strong&gt;14&lt;/strong&gt;&lt;/u&gt; - 14&amp;nbsp;&lt;u&gt;&lt;strong&gt;+ 2&lt;/strong&gt;&lt;/u&gt; = ?&lt;/p&gt;

&lt;p style=&quot;color: rgb(33, 37, 41);&quot;&gt;&amp;rArr; &lt;b&gt;&lt;u&gt;16 - 14 &lt;/u&gt;&lt;/b&gt;=&lt;b&gt; 2&lt;/b&gt;&lt;/p&gt;

&lt;p style=&quot;color: rgb(33, 37, 41);&quot;&gt;Hence, the correct answer is&amp;nbsp;&lt;span style=&quot;font-weight: 700;&quot;&gt;&amp;quot;Option 4&amp;quot;&lt;/span&gt;.&lt;/p&gt;

&lt;p&gt;&lt;img alt=&quot;&quot; src=&quot;//storage.googleapis.com/tb-img/production/24/08/6203fea433474e3b330f0951_22-7-22_Shashi%20Savita_D1.png&quot; style=&quot;width: 368px; height: 193px;&quot; /&gt;&lt;/p&gt;

&lt;p&gt;Given equation:&amp;nbsp;&lt;strong&gt;209 &amp;divide; 2 + 14 - 120 &amp;times; 3 = ?&lt;/strong&gt;&lt;/p&gt;

&lt;table border=&quot;1&quot; cellpadding=&quot;1&quot; cellspacing=&quot;1&quot; style=&quot;width:300px;&quot;&gt;
	&lt;tbody&gt;
		&lt;tr&gt;
			&lt;td style=&quot;text-align: center;&quot;&gt;&lt;strong&gt;Sign&lt;/strong&gt;&lt;/td&gt;
			&lt;td style=&quot;text-align: center;&quot;&gt;+&lt;/td&gt;
			&lt;td style=&quot;text-align: center;&quot;&gt;&amp;times;&lt;/td&gt;
		&lt;/tr&gt;
		&lt;tr&gt;
			&lt;td style=&quot;text-align: center;&quot;&gt;&lt;strong&gt;Interchange with&lt;/strong&gt;&lt;/td&gt;
			&lt;td style=&quot;text-align: center;&quot;&gt;-&lt;/td&gt;
			&lt;td style=&quot;text-align: center;&quot;&gt;&amp;divide;&lt;/td&gt;
		&lt;/tr&gt;
	&lt;/tbody&gt;
&lt;/table&gt;

&lt;p&gt;After interchanging the signs, the equation we get:&amp;nbsp;&lt;span style=&quot;color: rgb(33, 37, 41);&quot;&gt;209 &lt;/span&gt;&lt;span style=&quot;color: rgb(33, 37, 41); text-align: center;&quot;&gt;&amp;times;&lt;/span&gt;&lt;span style=&quot;color: rgb(33, 37, 41);&quot;&gt;&amp;nbsp;2 -&amp;nbsp;14 +&amp;nbsp;120 &amp;divide;&amp;nbsp;3 = ?&lt;/span&gt;&lt;/p&gt;

&lt;p&gt;&lt;span style=&quot;color: rgb(33, 37, 41);&quot;&gt;&amp;rarr;&amp;nbsp;209&amp;nbsp;&lt;/span&gt;&lt;span style=&quot;color: rgb(33, 37, 41); text-align: center;&quot;&gt;&amp;times;&lt;/span&gt;&lt;span style=&quot;color: rgb(33, 37, 41);&quot;&gt;&amp;nbsp;2 -&amp;nbsp;14 +&amp;nbsp;&lt;strong&gt;120 &amp;divide;&amp;nbsp;3&lt;/strong&gt; = ?&lt;/span&gt;&lt;/p&gt;

&lt;p&gt;&lt;span style=&quot;color: rgb(33, 37, 41);&quot;&gt;&amp;rarr;&amp;nbsp;&lt;strong&gt;209&amp;nbsp;&lt;/strong&gt;&lt;/span&gt;&lt;strong&gt;&lt;span style=&quot;color: rgb(33, 37, 41); text-align: center;&quot;&gt;&amp;times;&lt;/span&gt;&lt;/strong&gt;&lt;span style=&quot;color: rgb(33, 37, 41);&quot;&gt;&lt;strong&gt;&amp;nbsp;2&lt;/strong&gt; -&amp;nbsp;14 + 40 = ?&lt;/span&gt;&lt;/p&gt;

&lt;p&gt;&lt;span style=&quot;color: rgb(33, 37, 41);&quot;&gt;&amp;rarr; &lt;strong&gt;418&lt;/strong&gt;&amp;nbsp;-&amp;nbsp;14 &lt;strong&gt;+ 40 &lt;/strong&gt;= ?&lt;/span&gt;&lt;/p&gt;

&lt;p&gt;&lt;span style=&quot;color: rgb(33, 37, 41);&quot;&gt;&amp;rarr; 458 - 14 = ?&lt;/span&gt;&lt;/p&gt;

&lt;p&gt;&lt;span style=&quot;color: rgb(33, 37, 41);&quot;&gt;&amp;rarr; 444 = ?&lt;/span&gt;&lt;/p&gt;

&lt;p&gt;Hence, the correct answer is &lt;strong&gt;&amp;quot;444&amp;quot;&lt;/strong&gt;.&lt;/p&gt;

&lt;p style=&quot;color: rgb(33, 37, 41);&quot;&gt;Given:&amp;nbsp;&lt;strong&gt;15 December 2006&lt;/strong&gt;&lt;span style=&quot;font-weight: bolder;&quot;&gt;&amp;nbsp;was Friday&lt;/span&gt;.&lt;/p&gt;

&lt;p style=&quot;color: rgb(33, 37, 41);&quot;&gt;Now,&lt;/p&gt;

&lt;p style=&quot;color: rgb(33, 37, 41);&quot;&gt;2006&amp;nbsp;to 2009&amp;nbsp;= 3&amp;nbsp;Years (2 Ordinary Years and 1 Leap Year).&lt;/p&gt;

&lt;p style=&quot;color: rgb(33, 37, 41);&quot;&gt;And, In 3&amp;nbsp;Years = 1&amp;nbsp;Leap year and 2&amp;nbsp;Ordinary Years.&lt;/p&gt;

&lt;p style=&quot;color: rgb(33, 37, 41);&quot;&gt;So, 1 Leap Year has 2 odd days,&lt;/p&gt;

&lt;p style=&quot;color: rgb(33, 37, 41);&quot;&gt;And, 2&amp;nbsp;Ordinary Years&amp;nbsp;have 2&amp;nbsp;odd days.&lt;/p&gt;

&lt;p style=&quot;color: rgb(33, 37, 41);&quot;&gt;Total odd days = 2 + 2&amp;nbsp;= 4.&lt;/p&gt;

&lt;p style=&quot;color: rgb(33, 37, 41);&quot;&gt;then,&amp;nbsp;&lt;span style=&quot;font-weight: bolder;&quot;&gt;15 December 2009&amp;nbsp;will be Friday + 4&amp;nbsp;= Tuesday&lt;/span&gt;.&lt;/p&gt;

&lt;p style=&quot;color: rgb(33, 37, 41);&quot;&gt;Now, the number of days between&amp;nbsp;&lt;span style=&quot;&quot;&gt;15 December 2006&lt;/span&gt;&amp;nbsp;to&amp;nbsp;13 October 2009&lt;/p&gt;

&lt;p style=&quot;color: rgb(33, 37, 41);&quot;&gt;= 16 (December 2006) + 365 (2007) + 366 (2008, leap year) + 286 (days from Jan to Oct 13, 2009) = 1033 days.&lt;/p&gt;

&lt;p style=&quot;color: rgb(33, 37, 41);&quot;&gt;= 1033&amp;nbsp;days&amp;nbsp;&amp;rarr; 1033/7 = 147 weeks and 4&amp;nbsp;odd days.&lt;/p&gt;

&lt;p style=&quot;color: rgb(33, 37, 41);&quot;&gt;So,&amp;nbsp;&lt;strong&gt;&lt;span style=&quot;color: rgb(33, 37, 41);&quot;&gt;13 October 2009&lt;/span&gt;&lt;/strong&gt;&lt;span style=&quot;font-weight: bolder;&quot;&gt; will be&amp;nbsp;&lt;/span&gt;&lt;span style=&quot;color: rgb(33, 37, 41); font-weight: 700;&quot;&gt;Friday&amp;nbsp;&lt;/span&gt;&lt;span style=&quot;font-weight: bolder;&quot;&gt;+ 4&amp;nbsp;= Tuesday.&lt;/span&gt;&lt;/p&gt;

&lt;p style=&quot;color: rgb(33, 37, 41);&quot;&gt;Hence, the correct answer is&amp;nbsp;&lt;span style=&quot;font-weight: bolder;&quot;&gt;&amp;quot;Option 4&amp;quot;&lt;/span&gt;.&lt;/p&gt;

&lt;p style=&quot;color: rgb(33, 37, 41);&quot;&gt;The correct mirror image of the given figure is:&lt;/p&gt;

&lt;p style=&quot;color: rgb(33, 37, 41);&quot;&gt;&lt;img alt=&quot;&quot; src=&quot;//storage.googleapis.com/tb-img/production/24/12/F1_SSC_Priya_13_12_24_D65.png&quot; /&gt;&lt;/p&gt;

